<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />Our heart has not turned back;</para>

<para style="q1">our steps have not gone from your way.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />Yet you have severely broken us in the place of jackals</para>

<para style="q1">and covered us with the shadow of death.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />If we have forgotten the name of our God</para>

<para style="q1">or spread out our hands to a strange god,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />would not God search this out?</para>

<para style="q1">For he knows the secrets of the heart.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Indeed, for your sake we are being killed all day long;</para>

<para style="q1">we are considered to be sheep for the slaughter.</para>
